@anchor{g-value-set-enum}
@deffn Method g-value-set-enum g-value (id <integer>)
@deffnx Method g-value-set-enum g-value (sym <symbol>)

Returns nothing.

Sets the content of @var{g-value} to @var{id}, or to the id
